t, and a self-diagnostic command input unit for recognizing signals to check whether or not the device is operating normally, a shade level, a sensitivity level, a delay level, and a remaining battery charge by user's direct selection, operation, or adjustment, and inputting the recognized signals to the control unit.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>